snippet.title: Wylde Flowers - Official Trailer | Wholesome Direct 2023
snippet.description:
Join Tara on a journey to become a witch in Wylde Flowers, available now on Nintendo Switch, Apple Arcade, and Steam. Watch the latest trailer for another look at the world, characters, and more from this life simulation game.

#GameTrailers #SoG #Gaming
